    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment is accepted. Quantitative output comparisons demonstrate that all three QoIs fall within the pre-established 10% acceptance bound and E/uval < 1.96. The ensemble of FEA models from three independent organizations produced consistent predictions. The Test conditions factor did not achieve its required level (achieved 2, required 3); however, the assessment team judged that the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol and N=11 sample size across two laboratories provide sufficient confidence for a Medium model risk, Medium assurance level determination. Several factors were reviewed and found satisfactory without detailed level-by-level engagement in this record.",
